training/notebooks/
training/_DEV_NOTES.md

# Track the unified-v1 labels JSONL — irreproducible research artifact (190
# hand-labeled tiles via inline Claude Code labeling, plus 19 validation tiles
# documented in docs/UNIFIED_VLM_VALIDATION.md). Images + derived train/eval
# JSONLs stay ignored (regenerable via fetch_unified_corpus.py +
# build_unified_v{1,2}_sft_dataset.py with seed=42). Negations only work when
# the parent dir is also re-included, so we whitelist the file path explicitly.
!training/data/
training/data/*
!training/data/unified_v1/
training/data/unified_v1/*
!training/data/unified_v1/labels.jsonl

# Vendored references — separate upstream git repos, not part of this codebase.
# The orchestrator hits a self-hosted Cloud Run SimSat (URL hardcoded in
# agentic_eo/simsat_client.py; override via SIMSAT_BASE_URL env var). Clone
# the upstream simulator locally only if you want it running on your own box:
#   git clone https://github.com/DPhi-Space/SimSat
SimSat/
training/reference/

# Logs
*.log

# Slideshow + benchmark cache (local-only, may contain in-progress narrative).
